Class FindBinding

  • java.lang.Object
    • jeus.uddi.v3.AbstractRegistryObject
      • jeus.uddi.v3.api.request.inquiry.FindBinding
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, RegistryObject

    public class FindBinding
extends AbstractRegistryObject
    find_binding의 data type class. Used to locate bindings within or across one or more registered businessServices.
